cn.releaseNotes:
- changes in visual design: playback tempo is now controlled by a new Tempo knob on the bottom panel;
- 23 new modes added to the library;
- Added Reverb effect the harmony sounds (adjustable on the Settings page);
- Metronome feature renamed to Metrotone, as in all other our apps;
- you can now choose between 5 different metrotone click sounds on the Settings page;
- added support for the new iPhone display models;
- minor bug fixes.

